Thanx for opening topic <br>
<br>
There are several options for multiplayer, like BG, Vampire and even more (Myth/Quake...   ok, not quite)...<br>
<br>
The single-player story is very one-character oriented (Isador). So for the whole game to multiplay like BG, we (or some else, enthusiastic enough; see: MOD community and editors stuff in there...) will have to lighten it up and make some modifications. But, yes, anyone can script a multiplayer campaign within existing levels even without model and level editor.<br>
<br>
Or, one can script a single quest for multiplayer and add tons of enemies to have fun with players' party.<br>
<br>
Or coose one arena (level) and play DM.<br>
<br>
Or choose a level and play one Harvester (the character who traps and releases NMCs) against the team of other players. AvP has an interesting game with a predator against others; and whoever kills a predator, becomes one. In MistMare that could be called Isador (or Harvester) tag...<br>
<br>
Or choose an arena and all players are harvesters and play a RTS like myth, with one whole little army of NMCs each.<br>
<br>
As said: everything above is possible even without level and model editor, only using game database editor. We'll do some campaigns (co-op, DM, tag,...) ourselves, when we'll have some time...<hr></blockquote><!--EZCODE QUOTE END-->Should appeal to people who are still waiting for NWN but we'll see.  Demo is due out soon for it. <p></p><i></i></td></tr></table><table border=0 width=95%><tr><td align=left valign="top"> </td><td align=right valign="top"><a href="http://pub13.ezboard.com/fbrellserilisfrm58.showPrevMessage?topicID=1074.topic"> << Prev Topic</a>&nbsp;| <a href="http://pub13.ezboard.com/fbrellserilisfrm58.showNextMessage?topicID=1074.topic"> Next Topic >> </a><br><br><a self href=http://pub13.ezboard.com/fbrellserilisfrm58.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=1074.topic&index=1><img src=http://home.attbi.com/~eqmaximus/brell/addreply.jpg border=0 alt="Add Reply"></a> </td></tr></table><br><table width=95% border=0><td valign="top"><a href=http://pub13.ezboard.com/fbrellserilisfrm58.threadControl?topicID=1074.topic><img src=http://home.attbi.com/~eqmaximus/brell/del1.gif border=0 alt="Topic Control Image"> Topic Commands (Moderator only)</a><br> <a href=http://pub13.ezboard.com/fbrellserilisfrm58.subscribeUnregisteredToTopic?topicID=1074.topic>Subscribe</a> Click to receive email notification of replies<br>  <a href=http://pub13.ezboard.com/fbrellserilisfrm58.unsubscribeUnregisteredToTopic?topicID=1074.topic>Unsubscribe</a> Click to stop receiving email notification of replies<br> </td><td align="right" valign="top"></td></tr><tr align="right"><td colspan=2><form action=http://pub13.ezboard.com/BBSForum.jumpShowForum method=post><table border="0" cellspacing="0" cellpadding="1"><tr><td><b>jump to:</b><select name=forumName><option value="brellserilisfrm70">News and Events<option value="brellserilisbrellserilisdiscussion">The Commons (General EQ Discussion)<option value="brellserilisfrm58">The Outer Realm (Off T